		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message27943069">This thread is for the discussion of <!--link--><a href="http://myanimelist.net/anime/1729/">Maria-sama ga Miteru 3rd</a>.<br />
